subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams, in a rematch of the 2012 women’s final, defeated Victoria Azarenka, 7-5, 6-7 (6), 6-1, to win her 17th Grand Slam singles title, including five at the U.S. Open.
